# Code Style — Clean Code

> Quality bar: senior OSS library — small surface, high trust.

## Functions

- ~30 lines max (split when readability gains)
- Max 3 params → use input interface
- Early return; guard clauses first
- One abstraction level per function

## SOLID + DRY

- **S** — parsers parse; client orchestrates; transport sends
- **O** — new operations via new methods/parsers, not transport forks
- **L** — error subclasses substitutable for `CorreiosError`
- **I** — small `SoapTransport` interface
- **D** — client depends on transport abstraction; inject in tests
- **DRY** — shared builders in one module; no duplicated SOAP mapping

## Naming

| Kind | Convention |
|------|------------|
| Files | `kebab-case.ts` |
| Functions, vars | `camelCase` |
| Types, classes | `PascalCase` |
| Constants | `SCREAMING_SNAKE` or `camelCase` for config keys |

## Errors

- Use typed errors from `errors.ts`
- No silent catch — wrap with `CorreiosTransportError` etc.
- Parsers: handle Correios in-body error codes explicitly

## Comments

- Why, not what
- JSDoc on all public exports

## TypeScript

- `unknown` at SOAP boundaries; narrow in parsers
- No commented-out code in merged PRs
- No `TODO` without issue link